Package: T2C
Title: Takes HOMER tags to create a restriction fragment-sized bins to turn them into contact matrix
Version: 0.0.0.9001
Author: Aleksandra Cabaj
Maintainer: Aleksandra Cabaj <olacabaj@gmail.com>
Description: Takes T2C tags generated by HOMER and reference genome cut by matching restriction enzyme to create a restriction fragment-sized bins. Generates a contact matrix and plots it in the form of heatmap.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
Imports: 
    assertthat,
    heatmap3,
    utils,
    grDevices
Suggests:
  testthat
